{
    "title": "Águas de Março",
    "artist": "Tom Jobim",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Intro]</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 1 de 2   </span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 2 de 2</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte] </span>\n\n                              \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pau, é pedra</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim do caminho</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>              \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um resto de toco</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um pouco sozinho</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(11+)\">F7(11+)</span>              \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um caco de vidro, é a vida</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7M(13)\">E7M(13)</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o Sol, É a noite, é a morte </span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)\">B7M(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o laço, é o anzol</span>\n\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>       \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É peroba do campo</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o nó da madeira</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Caingá, candeia, é o Matita Pereira</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É madeira de vento</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tombo da ribanceira</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o mistério profundo</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o queira ou não queira</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>       \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o vento ventando </span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim da ladeira                             </span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a viga, é o vão</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Festa da cumeeira</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>        \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a chuva chovendo</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É conversa ribeira</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>                  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Das águas de março</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)\">B7M(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim da canseira</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte] </span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o pé, é o chão, é a marcha estradeira</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Passarinho na mão, pedra de atiradeira</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>         \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma ave no céu</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma ave no chão</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>            \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um regato, é uma fonte</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um pedaço de pão</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>      \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fundo do poço</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim do caminho</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No rosto, o desgosto</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um pouco sozinho</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Terceira Parte] </span>\n\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um estrepe, é um prego</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma ponta, é um ponto</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um pingo pingando </span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma conta, é um conto</span>\n\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um peixe, é um gesto</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>     \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma prata brilhando</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a luz da manhã, é o tijolo chegando</span>\n\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>     \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a lenha, é o dia</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim da picada</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a garrafa de cana</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O estilhaço na estrada</span>\n\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>      \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o projeto da casa</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o corpo na cama</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o carro enguiçado</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a lama, é a lama</span>\n\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um passo, é uma ponte</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um sapo, é uma rã</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um resto de mato, na luz da manhã</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>     \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">São as águas de março </span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fechando o verão</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a promessa de vida no teu coração</span>\n\n[Solo] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/D#\">F/D#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>  \n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(11+)\">F7(11+)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7M(13)\">E7M(13)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6\">B6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>  \n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb9/F\">Bb9/F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Solo]</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 1 de 4</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/D#\">F/D#</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 2 de 4</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(11+)\">F7(11+)</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 3 de 4</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7M(13)\">E7M(13)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6\">B6</span>  \n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 4 de 4</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb9/F\">Bb9/F</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Quarta Parte] </span>\n\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(13)\">B7(13)</span>                    \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É uma cobra, é um pau</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É João, é José</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>                \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um espinho na mão</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um corte no pé</span>\n\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">São as águas de março </span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fechando o verão</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a promessa de vida no teu coração</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Quinta Parte] </span>\n\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>                \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É pau, é pedra</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o fim do caminho</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um resto de toco</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um pouco sozinho</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um passo, é uma ponte</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#/B\">D#/B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um sapo, é uma rã</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/B\">C/B</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É um belo horizonte, é uma febre terçã</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#/B\">D#/B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">São as águas de março fechando o verão</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/B\">C/B</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a promessa de vida no teu coração</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Au, edra, im, minho</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Esto, oco, ouco, inho</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aco, idro, ida,   ol, oite, orte</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aço, zol</span>\n\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">São as águas de março </span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fechando o verão</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a promessa de vida no teu coração</span>\n\n[Final] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m6\">G#m6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6/G\">Em6/G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7M(9)/F#\">B7M(9)/F#</span>  \n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9)\">B7(9)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)/F\">B6(9)/F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em6\">Em6</span>  \n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B6(9)\">B6(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#/B\">D#/B</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/B\">C/B</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Final]</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E|------------------------------------------------|</span>\n",
